{"tid":2160838,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"壹傳媒股價持續受壓 散戶高追一殼眼淚","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T08:35:09.000Z","uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4442258b215192673988da0e3411ece120f9ecfa","tid":2160838,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒(00282)股價周一(17日)持續受壓，即市低位見0.36港元，跌10%；中午收報0.375元，跌6.25%，成交逾2,651萬元。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒主席黎智英上周一(10日)涉違反《港區國安法》而被拘捕，當日壹傳媒股價開始大幅異動，波動更持續至整個星期，由歷史低位0.075元炒至1.96元，成交大增，惟之後又急速滑落，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不少在高位追入的散戶叫苦。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黎智英在接受彭博訪問時着投資者不要買入壹傳媒股票，指因公司的基本面無法支持最近的上漲趨勢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港交易所發言人指，不評論個別公司或其股價走勢。所有香港上市公司必須遵守《上市規則》。香港交易所一直監察市場，致力確保執行有關規則時的全面性、公平性和透明度。"},{"pid":"288f61ca9d1fcc2c7ad7453a27f3ef7f48fc7ed6","tid":2160838,"uid":59920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:27:49.000Z","msg":"肥佬泥都有叫手足唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93b20234f35551386700502b6408898703d63b1","tid":2160838,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"In 水哥 We trust ！"},{"pid":"d6ca76b3802ea428dc7f8daad4121763c089277b","tid":2160838,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93b20234f35551386700502b6408898703d63b1","tid":2160838,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"In 水哥 We trust ！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"手足已成kingdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />